{"article_id":"v9lm328K5kZMi7QY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Florida ' s gubernatorial general election isn ' t even a day old ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"but it has already found its first controversy","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"after Republican Ron DeSantis claimed","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that his opponent , Tallahassee Mayor Andrew Gillum","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"- potentially the state ' s first black governor -","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"would \" monkey this up \"","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"if he wins in November .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"DeSantis ' s comments came during a Wednesday morning interview on Fox News","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"after winning the primary on Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"While discussing his Democratic opponent ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"DeSantis also called Gillum \" articulate , \" a term","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"often used","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to backhandedly compliment black people","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"whose intelligence seems surprising or out of the ordinary .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" This is a guy who ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"although he ' s much too liberal for Florida","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"- I think","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"he ' s got huge problems with how he ' s governed Tallahassee -","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"you know ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"he is an articulate spokesman for those far-left views ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"and he ' s a charismatic candidate , \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"DeSantis said .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"He continued :","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" The last thing","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"we need to do","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"is to monkey this up","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"by trying to embrace a socialist agenda with huge tax increases","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and bankrupting the state .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"That is not gon na work .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"That ' s not gon na be good for Florida . \"","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Uh Ron DeSantis just said","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"FL should n't `` monkey this up ''","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"by electing Andrew Gillum","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"pic.twitter.com/nDPp3Hx7zc","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"- Steve Morris","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"( @ stevemorris__ )","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"August 29 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Shortly after the remarks , Fox News host Sandra Smith made an on-air statement ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that \" we do not condone this language. \"","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Smith also directed viewers to a statement","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that DeSantis ' s spokesman issued shortly after the interview","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that attempted to clarify the remarks .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Gillum also responded to the remarks during an appearance on Fox News Wednesday afternoon ,","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that the comments showed","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that \" DeSantis was taking a page directly from the campaign manual of Donald Trump . \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"he ' s got another thing coming to him","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"if he thinks","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Florida voters are going to respond to that level of derision and division , \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Gillum added .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"DeSantis ' s remarks ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"just hours after President Donald Trump publicly criticized Gillum for crime in Tallahassee ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"suggest","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"that Republicans are wasting no time","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"in going after the Democrat .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"But the Fox News remarks are also causing critics to argue","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"that DeSantis is turning to racist attacks","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to draw a distinction between himself and his opponent .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"It ' s an issue","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"that often affects candidates of color , particularly those","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"running in states with sizable white populations .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"DeSantis ' s \" monkey \" comment shows how politicians use coded","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"- and not so coded -","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"language","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"to talk about race","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"Shortly after making the comments ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"a DeSantis spokesperson attempted to defuse the situation","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"by telling NBC News ' Ali Vitali","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that the Republican candidate regularly uses the term","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to refer to \" something","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that was messed up or not done right . \"","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"According to the spokesperson ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"the comment \" had nothing to do with race or anything like that . \"","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"In an additional statement to CNN , DeSantis communications director Stephen Lawson said","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"that the candidate was \" obviously talking about Florida","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"not making the wrong decision","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"to embrace the socialist policies","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that Andrew Gillum espouses . \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" To characterize it as anything else is absurd , \"","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"he added .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"But DeSantis ' s comments fit into an extensive history","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"of calling black people monkeys or primates .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"References to African Americans as apes and monkeys have long been invoked","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"to dehumanize them","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"and justify their treatment as second-class citizens .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"The trope was heavily used against President Barack Obama , his wife Michelle , and other members of his White House .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"At times , these sorts of associations are plainly made .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"But in other instances they are said much more subtly .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"As my colleague German Lopez has noted ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"these types of remarks","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"- often referred to as coded language -","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"are \" used against a group or idea","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that threatens traditional power structures. \"","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Coded language has long been wielded against African Americans","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"to cast them as deviant and different from whites ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"serving as an alternative for more direct language","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"that would immediately be considered offensive .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"\" Current racial code operates","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"by appealing to deep-seated stereotypes of groups","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that are perceived as threatening , \"","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Ian Haney-López , a professor at the University of California Berkeley , told in 2016 .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"because coded language does not rely on direct references to race ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"\" It allows people to say ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"' Hey , I ' m just criticizing the behavior ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"not criticizing a racially defined group . ' \"","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Haney-Lopez notes","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that coded language ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"which has been used","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"to criticize everything from immigrants to Black Lives Matter in recent years ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"is heavily used by politicians .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"\" Almost every conversation on the right has as a subtext an indication of race , \"","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"no matter how DeSantis views his own comments ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"his critics will not be as willing to remove them from this broader context .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"\" It ' s disgusting that Ron DeSantis is launching his general election campaign with racist dog whistles , \"","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Florida Democratic Party Chair Terrie Rizzo said in an emailed statement to BuzzFeed .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":183,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":157,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":150,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":129,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":122,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":126,"right":127,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":2,"right":125,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":6,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":133,"right":148,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":9,"right":132,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":10,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":11,"right":130,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elabor